Argued and submitted June 11, resubmitted In Banc October 10, In the Matter of the Adoption of I.M., a Minor Child, by M. and G., Appellants. (89C-40063; CA A62907) 802 P2d 101 Katherine Brown, Portland, argued the cause for appellants. With her on the brief were Hoevet, Snyder & Miller, P.C., Katherine Tennyson and Tennyson & Wine-miller, Portland.

affirmed by an equally divided court December 19, 1990
